  "detailed_description": "<strong>DUSTNET</strong> is an asymmetrical experience, join as a <strong>PC</strong>, <strong>VR</strong>, or <strong>AR</strong> player, enter the ruins of <i>de_dust2</i> and rebuild.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/310784f21b09b6006682d4e2ce673c64.?t=1620716006\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/310784f21b09b6006682d4e2ce673c64.poster.avif?t=1620716006\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY IN AUGMENTED REALITY FOR FREE</strong></h2>Visit the DUSTNET website to download the mobile AR companion app.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/68b7666562615278edeb2f1e6c2c149b.poster.avif?t=1620716006\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/68b7666562615278edeb2f1e6c2c149b.webm?t=1620716006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as a COMPUTER, VIRTUAL REALITY, or AUGMENTED REALITY player and join DUSTNET, each platform is its own unique player type in this experimental multiplayer server.<br></li><li>Explore the ruins of DUSTNET, unlock bhop, noclip, teleport, and other admin commands.<br></li><li>Join with your friends in VR & AR to edit the map and server, choose to be a competitive or cooperative player.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>DUSTNET</strong> is an asymmetrical experience, join as a <strong>PC</strong>, <strong>VR</strong>, or <strong>AR</strong> player, enter the ruins of <i>de_dust2</i> and rebuild.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/310784f21b09b6006682d4e2ce673c64.?t=1620716006\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/310784f21b09b6006682d4e2ce673c64.poster.avif?t=1620716006\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY IN AUGMENTED REALITY FOR FREE</strong></h2>Visit the DUSTNET website to download the mobile AR companion app.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/68b7666562615278edeb2f1e6c2c149b.poster.avif?t=1620716006\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987290/extras/68b7666562615278edeb2f1e6c2c149b.webm?t=1620716006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as a COMPUTER, VIRTUAL REALITY, or AUGMENTED REALITY player and join DUSTNET, each platform is its own unique player type in this experimental multiplayer server.<br></li><li>Explore the ruins of DUSTNET, unlock bhop, noclip, teleport, and other admin commands.<br></li><li>Join with your friends in VR & AR to edit the map and server, choose to be a competitive or cooperative player.</li></ul>",
